news.title: Generate your own funds, Gujarat CM tells urban bodies
news.para: Patel convened a meeting of elected leaders of municipal corporations, municipalities and urban development authorities in Gandhinagar recently, and said that the system of the state government and Union government providing grants will gradually be phased out.

news.title: Nashik civic body brings 13,000 properties under tax net
news.para: “While 4,500 new properties brought under tax net were from Panchavati division, around 3,500 properties were from Cidco division,” said the official.

news.title: Nagpur civic body's rebate plan fails, only 40% pay property tax
news.para: The civic body’s data shows total demand of property tax increased to Rs950 crore in current financial year due to revaluation and reassessment drive carried out in last few years.
